  "detailed_description": "<strong>Coastal Defense</strong><br><br>Coastal Defense is a fast paced, casual top-down tower defense game inspired by real-world coastal defense structures. Buy and upgrade your coastal defenses to defeat incoming navies!<br><br><strong>Defend the beach!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/29b76dac7672f539925fb39caea6c569.poster.avif?t=1719685866\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/29b76dac7672f539925fb39caea6c569.webm?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/29b76dac7672f539925fb39caea6c569.mp4?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enemy vessels are coming for your beach! Destroy them with your defensive turrets or by calling in artillery!<br><br><strong>Buy and upgrade!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/5f9c3c60af6f1213c3e9b9951cefe22a.poster.avif?t=1719685866\" width=250 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/5f9c3c60af6f1213c3e9b9951cefe22a.webm?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>As you play, you will be given funding. Use this funding to buy and upgrade turrets!<br><br><strong>Increasing danger!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/c393690fe3d3a05a926655dbd24cf582.poster.avif?t=1719685866\" width=250 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/c393690fe3d3a05a926655dbd24cf582.webm?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/c393690fe3d3a05a926655dbd24cf582.mp4?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As the waves increase, be prepared to face tougher enemies. Brace yourself to fight the final Battleship at wave 15!<br><br>This game also features:<br>- High replayability<br>- Tracked statistics<br>- Unlockable hard mode<br><br>To play the game, you need to use a mouse and a keyboard. Controllers are not supported.<br><br>I hope you like it!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Coastal Defense</strong><br><br>Coastal Defense is a fast paced, casual top-down tower defense game inspired by real-world coastal defense structures. Buy and upgrade your coastal defenses to defeat incoming navies!<br><br><strong>Defend the beach!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/29b76dac7672f539925fb39caea6c569.poster.avif?t=1719685866\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/29b76dac7672f539925fb39caea6c569.webm?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/29b76dac7672f539925fb39caea6c569.mp4?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enemy vessels are coming for your beach! Destroy them with your defensive turrets or by calling in artillery!<br><br><strong>Buy and upgrade!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/5f9c3c60af6f1213c3e9b9951cefe22a.poster.avif?t=1719685866\" width=250 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/5f9c3c60af6f1213c3e9b9951cefe22a.webm?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>As you play, you will be given funding. Use this funding to buy and upgrade turrets!<br><br><strong>Increasing danger!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/c393690fe3d3a05a926655dbd24cf582.poster.avif?t=1719685866\" width=250 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/c393690fe3d3a05a926655dbd24cf582.webm?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657540/extras/c393690fe3d3a05a926655dbd24cf582.mp4?t=1719685866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As the waves increase, be prepared to face tougher enemies. Brace yourself to fight the final Battleship at wave 15!<br><br>This game also features:<br>- High replayability<br>- Tracked statistics<br>- Unlockable hard mode<br><br>To play the game, you need to use a mouse and a keyboard. Controllers are not supported.<br><br>I hope you like it!",
